These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
City: colone, hannover, liverpool, boston
1. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| City   | colone | boston | hannover | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, drawing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | collecting | sudoku | video-games | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Hobby   | chess | filmmaking | magic-tricks | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, musical, western, romance
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | satire | romance | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar, dunhill, bluemaster
1. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | prince | dunhill | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
City: boston, colone, miami, berlin
1. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| City   | miami | boston | berlin | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, july, march
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | march | january | july | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, sprite, juice
1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola | juice | tea |

