2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is chess-climbing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Hobby   | chess | chess-climbing | card-games | camping |

