.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, badminton, climbing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Sport   | badminton | cycling | climbing | ice-hockey |

