.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, april, august
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Birthday   | february | april | october | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, grey, green, ivory
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
3. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
4. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Color   | green | ivory | brown | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, rock, electronic, soul
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | d&b | electronic | rock |

