.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, bird, rabbit
1. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet   | rabbit | cat | bird | ferret |

