.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, modern, tower
1. the gothic-revival house is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the tower house is on the left or right of the modern house##3
3. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
5. the tower house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| House   | modern | tower | gothic-revival | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, gardening, photography
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | collecting | photography | gardening | video-games |

 